{"tid":2123770,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"參院通過《國防授權法》 倡「六項保證」  美部署邀台參加環太軍演","createTime":"2020-07-25T02:44:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-25T02:52:32.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f462b0242de5f8821ca8c4ede46e526703688337","tid":2123770,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T02:44:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200725/AIKZFRNOVAGA5AWOYEYRASURJE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200725%2FAIKZFRNOVAGA5AWOYEYRASURJE%2F&d=u6RaX9rkx0MxONw5VJESxZB82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=85c4618a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200725%2FAIKZFRNOVAGA5AWOYEYRASURJE%2F&h=cd8e12db\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200725/AIKZFRNOVAGA5AWOYEYRASURJE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n參院通過《國防授權法》 倡「六項保證」 <br />\n美部署邀台參加環太軍演<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】中美關係惡化加劇，美國參議院周四（23日）大比數通過2021財政年度《國防授權法》，建議美軍需具備阻止大陸迅速控制台灣造成「既成事實」的能力，邀請台灣參與環太平洋軍演。台灣總統府強調會強化台美間的安全合作。有軍事評論員認為，一旦美國正式邀請台灣參加環太平洋軍演，將進一步刺激大陸，增加中美在受爭議地區擦槍走火的機會。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：中共戰機深夜闖空域 台派多架軍機驅趕<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/t--uYwlrYRpF9SA3UknIXZgojRg=/190x119/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/4XILC7ER5O6RSW63IXQHM7XQIA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Ft--uYwlrYRpF9SA3UknIXZgojRg%3D%2F190x119%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F4XILC7ER5O6RSW63IXQHM7XQIA.gif&h=8e2b3c30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n台灣總統蔡英文（中）早前親臨漢光演練，展示國軍實力。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n繼眾議院後，由共和黨領導的參議院周四也表決通過參院版本，以86票贊成、14票反對，通過2021財政年度《國防授權法》，國防開支將增至7,405億美元（約5.7萬億港元），較上一財政年度增長約0.3%，包括為軍隊加薪3%，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/F3pvo5tOt7dJRu3dUn0cjOLZIu8=/190x119/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PEPIFVRSWPP6ZXY3F7XUBVXKYI.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FF3pvo5tOt7dJRu3dUn0cjOLZIu8%3D%2F190x119%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPEPIFVRSWPP6ZXY3F7XUBVXKYI.gif&h=406ffee9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國海軍列根號航母17日在南海航行。路透社<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/uVzSpFZZTDwsAskXZFU9s75HpUY=/190x119/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/T62VBMYXX2VH2JP6UV4UXK7L7I.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FuVzSpFZZTDwsAskXZFU9s75HpUY%3D%2F190x119%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FT62VBMYXX2VH2JP6UV4UXK7L7I.gif&h=6cef24ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大陸轟六等戰機（上）多次闖入台灣空域被驅離。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n提案倡制華武力攻台<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。。包括對台軍售與國防工業合作，確保台灣維持不對稱戰力戰略。法案也建議，邀請台灣參加環太平洋軍事演習（RIMPAC）等軍事訓練、增加美台高級軍事將領交流。環太平洋軍演由美國主導，每兩年舉行一次，將於下月在太平洋海域舉行，大陸被排除在軍演名單外，但早前有傳台灣有望以「觀察員」身份參加。<br />\n<br />\n法案又指，美軍應維持對抗以武力或其他形式危及台灣人民安全、社會或經濟制度的脅迫，包括拒讓大陸具備迅速控制台灣以造成「既成事實」（fait accompli）的能力。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。參眾兩院協商法案內容達成一致後，就能呈交總統特朗普簽署成法。台灣總統府回應，感謝參議院對台灣國防安全的重視與支持，將持續強化台美安全合作。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/v6nlFtXWGMxWk9svXluozZHPn2I=/190x121/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RYLGQXY5XLJZ5MFE7KMSPPQQJM.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fv6nlFtXWGMxWk9svXluozZHPn2I%3D%2F190x121%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRYLGQXY5XLJZ5MFE7KMSPPQQJM.gif&h=5e5019ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【台最新軍備】空軍新式高教機「勇鷹號」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/H0pkib9RI6TrIrJnVo8wLFD0Cmc=/190x121/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BBGLFUH7CPETMWCSQS3PHQPF7I.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FH0pkib9RI6TrIrJnVo8wLFD0Cmc%3D%2F190x121%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBBGLFUH7CPETMWCSQS3PHQPF7I.gif&h=090fadaf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【台最新軍備】雄風三型反艦導彈。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n解放軍雷州實彈演練<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。公告強調，此次打靶覆蓋範圍廣、彈藥威力大，擅自出海會有極大被誤炸傷的風險。<br />\n<br />\n軍事評論員黃東表示，一旦美國。。。。。。。。。。。，還會提供技術讓台灣自行生產，包括高精密度的導彈技術等。"},{"pid":"d9832988fb9977452c8e2c6b1e634dd2df0ae44a","tid":2123770,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T02:46:45.000Z","msg":"擦槍走火未<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n美帝就係想打<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d88fc43cb021c34eab053aa9c761f96cb3844e20","tid":2123770,"uid":127575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T02:47:45.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>China Joe : NO !!!!!!! 咁我點奶共 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span>"},{"pid":"466d984ee739ad21a8f904abac4d26698962f127","tid":2123770,"uid":248290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T02:49:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GatApxL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGatApxL.jpg&h=5125a561&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"285ba2adbb20006c4147b870a6496a76c54530ae","tid":2123770,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T02:52:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}